pageContext.claim: “The Florida Election should be called in favor of Rick Scott and Ron DeSantis in that large numbers of new ballots showed up out of nowhere, and many ballots are missing or forged. An honest vote count is no longer possible-ballots massively infected. Must go with Election Night!”
pageContext.analysis: What the president is describing is more counting than "finding." It takes time to count all the votes including absentee ballots. There's no evidence of voter fraud.
